title: Stake ETH to support $LEX liquidity?
body:
Should Coop. add to $LEX uniswap pool as liquidity providers? Our Coop. multisig at https://gnosis-safe.io/app/#/safes/0xEA693e18154C98cd9E3014C6Ba1e89956a929F4A/balances, currently has about ~$4000.

https://app.uniswap.org/#/swap?outputCurrency=0x63125c0d5Cd9071de9A1ac84c400982f41C697AE

This comes in context of a potential user / community member noting exchange was difficult to use due to low liquidity: https://twitter.com/JackMcDermott1/status/1334894236949475328?s=20
author: 0x1C0Aa8cCD568d90d61659F060D1bFb1e6f855A20
